nodes.text: The Kielty was a pair of Rebel BFF-1 bulk freighters that received cargo from the new Alliance members, the Habassa, who delievered it with freighters called Starmover.
During that time, the freighters were attacked by the Imperial EF76 Nebulon-B escort frigate Anjisan but Keyan Farlander warded off her attacks until the transfer was done.
